file.name: api.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 0.1.0
  title: Test

components:
  schemas:
    Foo:
      type: object
      properties:
        bar:
          oneOf:
            - type: string
            - type: integer
    Bar:
      oneOf:
        - type: string
        - type: integer

    Baz:
      oneOf:
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Foo"
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Bar"
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Person"

    Person:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        age:
          type: integer

    QueryResponseRowEntry:
      description: One field from query results
      nullable: true
      oneOf:
      - nullable: true
        type: string
      - type: boolean
      - type: number
